6 NOW, THEREFORE,
7 Be it resolved by the Senate of the General Assembly of the Commonwealth of
8 Kentucky:
9 Section 1. The Senate hereby expresses its profound sense of sorrow upon the
10 passing of Susan Maureen Brothers Mayo and extends heartfelt condolences to her
11 family, friends, and the Maysville community.
12 Section 2. When the Senate adjourns this day, it does so in honor and loving
13 memory of Susan Maureen Brothers Mayo.
14 Section 3. The Clerk of the Senate is directed to transit a copy of this
15 Resolution to Senator Cassie Chambers Armstrong for presentation to the family.
